Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.30,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KEESOKAN HARINYA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, rasanya ada yang kurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku perlu mengajukan\Nduet penyiksa saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah cek naskah pengajuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duet penyiksa ini cukup menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Referensi modelnya dari senior di kantorku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa orang seperti itu benar-benar ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong tulis berdasarkan\Nnaskah pengajuan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita bersihkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu suka bersih-bersih, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyenangkan melihat air\Ndi ember menjadi merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham maksudmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, hari ini tidak perlu bersih-bersih.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tim pembersih akan datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, kalian belum pernah bertemu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Lishe, petugas kebersihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia rutin membersihkan ruang penyiksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbisik...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menanyakan namamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia jarang menanyakan nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia suka padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lishe itu perempuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mau menerima pernyataan cintanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya, aku punya tiga kakak perempuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, perempuan itu merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, kasihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga putus dengan pacarmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putus, nyambung, lalu putus lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siklusnya tetap, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka yang datang dan pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya pernah punya satu pacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sangat populer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah selesai,\Njadi tolong tanda tanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ruangan itu sangat kotor,\Njadi tagihannya besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikan aku diskon, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelit sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pelit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis imut?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia manis sekali di balik topeng itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mike si penulis "Peluru Penyiksaan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu "Peluru Penyiksaan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Judul novel menarik yang kubaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tentang seorang penyiksa genius
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan muridnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, mirip aku dan Siu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama penulisnya juga Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yang menulis novel itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero dan yang lain memang jadi referensinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, hebat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelumnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Boleh pakai kalian sebagai referensi?\N- sudah diizinkan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tentu.\N- olehmu dan Siu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pernah menanyakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat suka novel ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengira akan bertemu penulisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditambah lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia gadis yang manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku minta kontakmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau pergi bersama lain kali?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lishe, kamu salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mike itu laki-laki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bertukar kontak saja sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon kerja samanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran kenapa dia\Ntiba-tiba sangat tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah ketemu Lishe lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, beberapa kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia agak kecewa saat tahu kamu laki-laki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya, aku ingin tahu lebih banyak\Ntentang industri pembersihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku menjadwalkan\Nwawancara lain dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, siapa sangka kalau kamu\Nakan disangka perempuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sudah biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kalau jadi maskulin,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin aku tidak akan terlalu disukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajah manis itu adalah senjatamu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang manis,\Njadi tolong belikan steik untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku akan mentraktirmu makan steik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini benar-benar aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada semacam konspirasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu suka tempat seperti ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang aku datang ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah bekerja di Spirytus,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku takut pergi ke kafe kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kucing sensitif terhadap bau.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, setelah memakai detergen\Nyang kamu sarankan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tidak perlu khawatir lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meskipun harganya agak mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas pembelianmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih! Aku akan menjaganya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menyimpannya\Ndi kotak antibakteri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketat banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mike, kamu ingin beralih jadi penulis tetap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perusahaanku juga menanyakan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang sulit bekerja dengan banyak sif,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kurasa aku tidak bisa berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tulisanku makin bagus\Nsejak mulai menyiksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menyeimbangkan keduanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua hal itu mungkin adalah takdirmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Klien utama kami adalah penyiksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ada beberapa permintaan individu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain pembersihan biasa,\Nada juga sisa perang antara geng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perang antara geng?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Industri pembersihan\Nternyata cukup mendalam, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaannya sendiri biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kutanya direktur kami\Napa aku boleh mengajakmu berkeliling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu pertama bertemu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu menganggapku perempuan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu agak kecewa waktu itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa karena kamu tidak suka pria?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya tidak suka pria,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku merasa lebih santai\Ndi dekat sesama jenis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka di dekat perempuan\Nkarena mereka manis dan harum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga berharap aku perempuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lebih baik tetap jadi Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu manis dan harum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kamu bisa lebih harum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wangi sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu suka pelembut pakaian kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pandai berjualan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kencanmu dengan Lishe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cuma pertemuan biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan membeli pelembut pakaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu gampang dirayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga pakai, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Produk mereka memang bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku terpaksa membelinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian dari Spirytus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada pria bernama Dobel, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa antar aku padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dobel adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero bertugas menyiksanya hari ini, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat bawa aku ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah bicara dengan direkturmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Manika, seorang pembunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembunuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, ada satu lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang, kami mendapat permintaan\Nuntuk menyiksa dan membunuh subjek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kontrak ganda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, bisa tolong masuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero, lama tidak bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacar Sero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantan pacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya kamu bekerja di area lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru pindah ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat serahkan orang itu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini waktu istirahatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana pertemuan pertama kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penghibur dan pelanggan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok malah di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami mulai berkencan\Nsetelah dia berhenti menjadi penghibur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah di Spirytus saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kebetulan bertemu dengannya di bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa lama kamu akan istirahat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin segera selesai dan pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua sangat terus terang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mereka masih punya perasaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subjek penyiksaan butuh waktu sendiri\Nuntuk merasa takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan segera mengurusnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manika, jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu masih mencintai Sero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria ini
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tampan, baik,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cakap, dan ingat semua hari jadi kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selera hadiahnya juga bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, dia tipe pria yang terus memakai\Nhadiah mantan pacarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa salahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu menyebalkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih memakai dompet pemberianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya tidak boleh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa harus kubuang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan dibuang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Babak kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mau mengaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah lebih baik jujur saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ikut campur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin masalah\Npenyebab kami putus belum berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa masalahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembunuhnya adalah mantan pacar Sero?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalahnya sudah muncul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengenalmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu satu-satunya pacar\Nyang dicampakkan Sero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hanya membicarakan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pekerjaan dan Siu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu semua karena pekerjaan dan kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mencampakkanmu karena ucapanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma sedikit kasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero jadi begitu karena ucapannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa bagusnya pekerjaan menyiksa\Npenjahat di ruang kecil ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita putus saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembunuh yang barbar, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada angin, ada pohonnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini alasannya aku benci dengan penyiksa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku tidak memaksanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sendiri tak masuk prioritasnya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu ini prioritas Sero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peringkat adiknya lebih tinggi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tahu pria seperti apa dia,\Naku tetap ingin diutamakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku sangat menyayanginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bahkan sekarang, aku masih...\N- Aku sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu dengar itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagian besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon, Sero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kita kembali bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manika, kamu itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cantik dan bertubuh bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dia juga elegan.\N- Kamu berlumuran darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pekerjaan kami sama-sama berdarah.\N- Sero, kamu juga berlumuran darah
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami punya banyak kesamaan\Ndan itu menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu yang paling lama bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kamu tidak bermaksud\Nmengatakan itu karena marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih peduli\Npada penyiksaan daripada pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero, kebetulan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tak bertemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacarku penting bagiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi pekerjaan dan diriku lebih penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya\Naku selalu putus dengan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita pasangan serasi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nkamu serius dengan ucapanmu tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku serius.\NBagaimana denganmu, Sero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mau berkencan denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, ayo berpacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu "oke"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Oke" ya "oke"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku harus bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku belum bisa ambil istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Siu ingin menemuiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maaf, hari ini aku...\N- Kumohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tinggalkan aku hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Manika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu alasan dia mencampakkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tetap saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena aku sangat menyukainya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tidak jadi masalah meresponsnya begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak jadi masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaan adalah hal paling penting bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pekerjaan hanya ada satu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi perempuan ada banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manika, kamu memukulnya dengan keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa terjadi sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noe,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}boleh aku berpose keren?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa saja boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu, kamu terlalu santai soal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan foto itu?\NApa yang akan kamu lakukan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuunggah\Ndi laman profil penyiksa kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu kita punya situs web.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang masih berupa desain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita punya rekrutan baru yang menjanjikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jadi bisa terima lebih banyak pekerjaan.\N- Dia bilang kita menjanjikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cara yang bagus untuk menunjukkan\Ndiri kita pada pencari kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kalian mau bekerja sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo kita berjuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merepotkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak mau membantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin bertanya kenapa kamu bergabung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin pekerjaan yang tidak melibatkan\Nbanyak interaksi dengan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangka pendek, pendapatan tinggi,\Ndan rasa ingin tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Singkat, padat, dan jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku belum pernah kerja di bidang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memilih yang belum pernah\Ndilakukan dan mengundinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang mencurigakan mendekatiku di gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hera...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasan Mike dan Hugh bagus,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi bisakah kita tambahkan\Nsedikit karakteristik?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Alasanmu yang terburuk.\N- Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kebanyakan orang\Nhanya mengikuti arus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu punya alasan\Nyang lebih proaktif?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu mengagumi pekerjaan interogasi\Natau ingin menyiksa orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah orang seperti itu berbahaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kenapa kamu terus\Nmelakukan pekerjaan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku berbakat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa menampilkan keduanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukan betapa kuatnya tubuh manusia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bagaimana beberapa bagian\Nbahkan bisa menekuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti berkunjung\Nke pameran anatomi tubuh manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pekerjaan yang menarik\Ndan menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tampak senang, tapi itu menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa mengorek kebenaran\Ndari semua makhluk kotor itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi kurasa itu pekerjaan yang berarti.\NAku berkontribusi pada masyarakat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar, tapi mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ditulis frontal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berusaha memperindahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cerdas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kita juga perlu\Nmemotret ruang penyiksaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah apa kita bisa menggunakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira Noe orang yang menakutkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sebenarnya dia orang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seharusnya cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas bantuan kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sangat bersemangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, hanya ini yang bisa kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu, hanya ada kita bertiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sekarang sangat ramai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah selesai memotret?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kenapa"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suap?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tulis "Tuan Sero adalah genius"\Ndi profilku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku tidak suka kopi hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak bisa minum kopi hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa meminumnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noe, kamu belum tidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku sudah mewawancarai mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku ingin menyusun\Nsemua hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas perhatianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lega melihatmu akrab\Ndengan semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu merasa seperti di tempat yang cocok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat yang cocok...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu memilikinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menciptakannya untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menyukainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggallah bersamaku dan jadilah keluargaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bodoh sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak tempat\Nagar kamu bisa merasa diterima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Spirytus bukan tempat\Nyang kuciptakan untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sesuatu\Nyang kamu ciptakan sendiri, Noe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hera.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teruslah menciptakan lebih banyak tempat\Nyang cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noe, kemarilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak suka dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kita mengusirnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa.
